{"tid":1036020,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［有片］英國人質問示威既中國留學生‘你哋喺度有言論自由，西藏係咪都應該有‘’我們好多人都討厭你哋既主席，佢係人權踐踏者‘","createTime":"2019-02-25T02:43:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-26T01:20:56.000Z","uid":48083,"like":885,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":82,"replies":[{"pid":"c7146a6c11feeb2a424e9fdbfa0968ca998b7b90","tid":1036020,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T02:43:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://mobile.twitter.com/vanessa_zhanguk/status/1099451937995542528\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmobile.twitter.com%2Fvanessa_zhanguk%2Fstatus%2F1099451937995542528&d=g2%2Fo6b0QjPi1xWtu1PcU8eNdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=25bb37f9\" target=\"_blank\">https://mobile.twitter.com/vanessa_zhanguk/status/1099451937995542528</a><br />\n<br />\n英國一路人騎車路過正在做擁共宣傳的中國留學生們。<br />\n<br />\n英：「你們在這裡表達言論自由，你們是否認為世界上所有人都應該有此權利？ 包括西藏和北京？」<br />\n中：「我們是中國人，我們只說中文，bye 」<br />\n<br />\n英：「我們英國很多人都非常討厭你們的主席，他是人權踐踏者。」<br />\n中：「我愛中國，我愛我的國家。」"},{"pid":"ffa933a26d9e57c626d7696c24ede051702cf310","tid":1036020,"uid":17646,"like":658,"dislike":0,"score":658,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T02:44:48.000Z","msg":"我愛中國，我愛我的國家<br />\n返中國啦"},{"pid":"ee6c5e663c3240f600021dd1ea4fc51c385cdba0","tid":1036020,"uid":191352,"like":501,"dislike":0,"score":501,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T02:47:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"365179a528131a08634d9d343b861209dbea24bf","tid":1036020,"uid":39796,"like":173,"dislike":1,"score":172,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T02:57:32.000Z","msg":"支那小丑"},{"pid":"1f837b459dbe5179f822189fa98e8917c7274f8a","tid":1036020,"uid":152476,"like":435,"dislike":2,"score":433,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T03:02:53.000Z","msg":"支那人最鍾意利用自由反自由"},{"pid":"92bdf1b2bcfd9c4a23194a157e3005604d143c64","tid":1036020,"uid":152476,"like":53,"dislike":4,"score":49,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T03:21:34.000Z","msg":"如果呢個post係屌香港留學生已經十幾廿頁"},{"pid":"ca74c40d7c85016930d31f0b5c6e17e499bd61d2","tid":1036020,"uid":51271,"like":131,"disli